column2: select aaa.id, s.ra, s.dec from (select max(ll.ew) as maxew, ss.specobjid as id from speclineall ll, specobj ss where ll.ew<># and ss.specobjid=ll.specobjid group by ss.specobjid) aaa, specobj s where maxew<# and s.specobjid=aaa.id and (sn_#># or sn_#># or sn_#>#) and (zstatus=# or zstatus=#) and zconf<#
